	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001049_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Hadley Green</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right"> 27<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi> June </p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1857 </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi></persName></p>
<lb/><p>Can you 
<lb/>lend me the letter 
<lb/>which contains 
<lb/>an account 
<lb/>of the waterfall 
<lb/>of the <placeName>Zambesi</placeName><reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I am at that 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001049_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>point now and 
<lb/>would like to 
<lb/>see it again 
<lb/>as I wrote 
<lb/>that description 
<lb/>with care<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>We came 
<lb/>straight home 
<lb/>on Thursday 
<lb/>and did not 
<lb/>sleep in <placeName>London</placeName><reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001049_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>We were well 
<lb/><choice><sic>recieved</sic><corr>received</corr></choice> but 
<lb/>I did not make 
<lb/>the acquaintance 
<lb/>of <persName>Acland</persName>. </p>
<lb/><p rend="center">I am Dear D<hi rend="sup">r</hi></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">Ever Yours
<persName>D. Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><p><choice><reg>T</reg><orig>t</orig></choice>hat ruffian <persName><w>Arrow-<lb break="no"/>smith</w></persName> is putting 
<lb/>all the blame 
<lb/>on his delay on me<reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001049_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'--> 
<lb/>Will you give 
<lb/>my <choice><sic>daguerrotype</sic><corr>daguerreotype</corr></choice>
<lb/>likeness which 
<lb/>was sent home 
<lb/>from <placeName>Loanda</placeName>
<lb/>by <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Gabriel</persName> to 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Brand</persName> - <persName>M<hi rend="sup">rs</hi>
<lb/>L.</persName> wishes to 
<lb/>return it as 
<lb/>it was only a loan 
<lb/>&amp; <persName>Brand</persName> will 
<lb/>send it to <persName>Gabriel</persName><reg>.</reg></p>
			
</div>
